edconsent\" target=\"_blank\">Rethinking Informed Consent in Bioethics</a>,</em>&nbsp;published in 2007. She was Principal of Newnham College, a college of the University of Cambridge, from 1992 to 2006, and President of the British Academy from 2005 to 2009. In early 2013 O&#39;Neill was confirmed as the new Chair of England&#39;s Equality and Human Rights Commission. She is a crossbench member of the House of Lords.</p>"}],"speaker_name":"Onora O'Neill","tags":["TEDx","global issues","government","philosophy","trust"],"title":"What we don't understand about trust","video_type":{"id":"2","name":"TEDx Talk"},"viewed_count":1561805}]}
